headline: Snap-on Incorporated (SNA): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Snap-on Incorporated on The Reservist’s Substack by Yehoshua Zlotogorski. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on SNA.
